        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar af = parseFloat(af);\nvar sp = parseFloat(sp);\nvar eratio = parseFloat(eratio);\nvar bmi = parseFloat(bmi);\nvar age = parseFloat(age);\n\nvar y = -9.19174463966566 + 0.0451129471272832*age + 0.130730156015681*bmi + 0.0858634402456586*eratio + 0.051963758732548*sp + 1.69968057294513*af;\n\nvar z = Math.pow(Math.E,y);\n\nvar prob = (z/(1 + z))*100; \n\nprob = prob.toFixed(1);\n\n//results\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: prob,\n    value_text: '%',\n    message: 'Probability of heart failure with preserved EF'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Prob',\n    value: prob,\n    value_text: '%',\n    message: 'Probability of heart failure with preserved EF'   \n});",
